```

To complete the task, here goes the unit test as below.

```perl
use Test::More;
use Test::Deep;

my $unit_tests = [
    { in  => { H => [2, 6, 4, 5, 1, 3],
               T => [1, 0, 2, 0, 1, 2],
             },
      out => [5, 1, 2, 6, 3, 4],
    },
];

foreach my $unit_test (@$unit_tests) {
    is_deeply(order_lineup($unit_test->{in}), $unit_test->{out});
}

done_testing;
```

